@startuml
title UC05 - Backend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class PredictionController { +submit(request): Response +update(id, request): Response }
class PredictionService { +submitOrUpdate(userId, dto): PredictionDto +assertMatchOpen(match): void }
class MatchRepository { +findById(id): Match }
class CriterionRepository { +findByMatch(id): List<PredictionCriterion> }
class PredictionRepository { +findByUserAndCriterion(userId, criterionId): Prediction +save(prediction): Prediction }
class StatisticsService { +updateVotes(matchId, criterionId): void }
PredictionController --> PredictionService
PredictionService --> MatchRepository
PredictionService --> CriterionRepository
PredictionService --> PredictionRepository
PredictionService --> StatisticsService
note bottom of PredictionService
  assertMatchOpen: chỉ cho dự đoán khi status = SCHEDULED
  (khóa khi bóng lăn / match_time). selected_team ∈ {HOME, AWAY}.
  unique(user_id, criterion_id) -> BR05.
  Có >= 1 dự đoán => user là participant của pool gold (tính khi FINISHED, xem UC06).
end note
@enduml
